{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130531, "create_time": 1653126912, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "快5年不学生物了，真的有点懵", "timestamp": 1653126912}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130532, "create_time": 1653126918, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "PCR検査", "timestamp": 1653126918}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130554, "create_time": 1653127672, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "实时荧光RT-PCR", "timestamp": 1653127672}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130560, "create_time": 1653127845, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "先逆转录，然后PCR，荧光标记，每轮测荧光量", "timestamp": 1653127845}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130587, "create_time": 1653128910, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "任何核酸相关的检测都必须PCR吧，不然量太少检查不出来", "timestamp": 1653128910}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130891, "create_time": 1653137337, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "提RNA，反转录成DNA，然后在温度梯度反应仪器里面，以DNA为模版，以新冠病毒序列为引物，反复复制，使其含量指数上升。核酸检测的PCR叫荧光定量PCR，是因为，每轮扩增时，都会镶嵌荧光染料，多轮扩增后，机器会检测到这个荧光信号。", "timestamp": 1653137337}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 130899, "create_time": 1653137472, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "如果被检测人体内本身没有病毒，那做扩增的时候，这个引物（新冠病毒序列）没有可结合的位置，就不能发生反复复制，自然也就不会有荧光信号的累加", "timestamp": 1653137472}], "create_time": 1653126885, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653137472, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 7, "pid": 45592, "poll": null, "reply": 7, "text": "小白求问：核酸检测的原理是啥啊，类似PCR那种吗", "timestamp": 1653126885}}